Code:

print("Check whether the given 
number is even / odd")
n=int(input("Enter a number: \n"))
if n%2==0:
    print(n," is a even number")
else:
    print(n," is a odd number")
           
Output:

Check whether the given number is even / odd
Enter a number: 
45  is a odd number

Check whether the given number is even / odd
Enter a number: 
4  is a even number
